Hi!

This is my first year in FRC. I downloaded the disc file for the 2024 WPILIB Download. We got the disc, but when we tried to open the installer, it said that we must install an app to run the installer, and it sent us to the windows store blank screen. We have already downloaded the most recent version of VS Code as well as the newest JDK, so we are not sure what other requirements we could be missing.

Thank you so much for your help! Have a great rest of your day!
